{"tid":1683871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【 傷11 】個post上左微博熱搜！緊張成咁，睇嚟我哋做啱咗。","createTime":"2019-10-30T23:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T02:44:52.000Z","uid":295155,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bb42bd38dbff9e9288a314d573949ef1b4d5edc0","tid":1683871,"uid":295155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:40:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.sina.cn/2019-10-30/detail-iicezuev6003389.d.html?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.cn%2F2019-10-30%2Fdetail-iicezuev6003389.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHjQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=e2b7a648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.cn/2019-10-30/detail-iicezuev6003389.d.html?from=wap</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KC1GSO5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKC1GSO5.png&h=c83f573c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1UFMjt6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1UFMjt6.png&h=e0f58704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">【絲打主場】【和理非打大佬】 【經濟行動POST 】 「雙11」一於幫佢「傷11」！罷買所有中國網購，尤其淘寶天貓 ！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>「雙11」一於幫佢「傷11」！罷買所有中國網購，尤其淘寶天貓 ！香港係2018年出口地區No.1，今年要佢得返一成！</strong><br />\n<br />\n初次開行動post，因為真係覺得無理由唔響佢做推廣時跟手罷一罷佢！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「雙11」係罷買紅店大佬「淘寶」既好時機！</strong><br />\n<br />\n跟據蘋果日報2018年報道：「除了中國本地搶購，境外的用戶都參與雙11購物節，根據阿里巴巴公佈的數據，香港是出口國家/地區第一位，然後分別是俄羅斯、美國、台灣及澳洲。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然萬聖節都未到，咁快講「雙11」好似時間尚早。但通常大約11月1號開始就有減價動靜，但由於出口地區頭幾名當中有美國同台灣，所以好想早啲可以Wecorrect埋一齊在「雙11」杯葛淘寶！有賴各位文宣組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，希望可以中英對照，Wecorrect 埋台灣美國一齊「傷11」！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算真係好需要到淘寶網購，都希望唔好貪個少少便宜，比少少骨氣，「雙11」之前或之後買。做低佢條大數據！<br />\n根據以往經驗，「雙11」除咗大陸網購，好多外國網站都會跟潮流，都係呢段時間做減價。要網購大把好選擇！<br />\n眼見NBA wecorrect如火如荼，希望今次行動會有多少回響～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30bacc6fd1c0796e69752837d6a48be2e66b8977","tid":1683871,"uid":21552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:41:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8fc94971a18d7342cf0cec896ee0d18c532e37c","tid":1683871,"uid":16250,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:41:53.000Z","msg":"解放軍突擊香港 又係死咗11個<br />\n<br />\n傷11<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0b5b4139f4ff840d7ced61fc8c251772643552","tid":1683871,"uid":241742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:41:54.000Z","msg":"睇真啲 好似串緊我地喎"},{"pid":"997112f85f082605d0edcc911a87b9f63f922bed","tid":1683871,"uid":109918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:41:58.000Z","msg":"罷買支那野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63ef44e6a836f25cf0e0d0ae517c50797618aa9","tid":1683871,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca470b713d3883e4a87b217402bb4771d49542a6","tid":1683871,"uid":280648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fd0b5b4139f4ff840d7ced61fc8c251772643552","tid":1683871,"uid":241742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:41:54.000Z","msg":"睇真啲 好似串緊我地喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:44:38.000Z","msg":"咁我哋將佢變做現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e50318991b318394aeea3f631d5b1bb9c12bbe","tid":1683871,"uid":295155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd0b5b4139f4ff840d7ced61fc8c251772643552","tid":1683871,"uid":241742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:41:54.000Z","msg":"睇真啲 好似串緊我地